text.tspan: To convert an infix expression to postfix, you can use the following algorithm:
2. Iterate over each symbol in the infix expression from left to right.
3. If the symbol is an operand (a number or variable), add it to the result string.
4. If the symbol is a left parenthesis '(', push it onto the stack.
5. If the symbol is a right parenthesis ')', pop symbols off the stack and add them
to the result string until a left parenthesis is encountered. Then discard the left parenthesis.
6. If the symbol is an operator (+, -, *, /, ^), compare its precedence with the precedence
of the top symbol on the stack. If the stack is empty or the top symbol is a left parenthesis,
push the operator onto the stack. Otherwise, pop symbols off the stack and add them to
the result string until an operator with lower precedence (or a left parenthesis) is encountered.
Then push the new operator onto the stack.
7. After all symbols have been processed, pop any remaining symbols off the stack and
add them to the result string.
